{"tid":1001360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"停拍AV賺更大！明日花F奶撐爆自家泳衣　網友卻冒黑人問號","createTime":"2019-01-30T05:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T11:15:55.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4357af04067aca94082f34ece3ea357cc01b1853","tid":1001360,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"日本AV界天后明日花綺羅從良「無限期休業」後，積極跨美妝界、電影界撈金，不但主演電影《鋼鐵女孩 FINAL WARS》，個人品牌Whip Bunny進攻潮流界更獲女性粉絲支持，就連日本女性整形指標排行榜，她都從上屆第三名升到冠軍，人氣事業更上層樓。<br />\n<br />\n近日，明日花在推特展示個人品牌Whip Bunny最新一季產品，她親自下海為擔任泳裝Model，只見她35F奶襯托白色蕾絲設計再配上頭飾秀色可餐，她並預告4月就會上市。雖然明日花大讚該款泳裝充滿洋娃娃風格，但網友卻一臉黑人問號？指這設計根本不是一件泳衣，頭上配飾也非泳帽，配搭相當古怪，還有人質疑能不能下水「根本就是情趣內衣嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/du5tkCY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdu5tkCY.png&h=5c893bae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FddKDpE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFddKDpE.png&h=87a0d113&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tD2vyXZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtD2vyXZ.png&h=4f61e9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDtR2Rk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDtR2Rk.png&h=d7f27753&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95a365c8c0f1d8e10dfcb741db3ade006b673241","tid":1001360,"uid":162783,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"全身都整 但好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5657ee3ee1d6bd22182e37f5c957346779a9dd0b","tid":1001360,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"95a365c8c0f1d8e10dfcb741db3ade006b673241","tid":1001360,"uid":162783,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"全身都整 但好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"極品肉便器<img src=\"/asset